</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>二手買賣平台現利是封炒賣潮，彭博：瑞銀利是封被炒至每個 10 元</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/27/facebook-marketplace-carousell/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-marketplace-carousell</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jan 2022 06:51:08 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1083259</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>農曆新年將至，「派利是」是華人地區的傳統文化。各大銀行推出應節利是封免費送給客戶，作為為即將到來的虎年帶來好運 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>農曆新年將至，「派利是」是華人地區的傳統文化。各大銀行推出應節利是封免費送給客戶，作為為即將到來的虎年帶來好運。據《彭博》報導，香港各投資銀行正向客戶免費派發的利是封，竟在香港二手市場平台炒買。</p><p>《彭博》統計各投資銀行，如 Facebook Marketplace 、 Carousell 等香港二手買賣平台平均每個利是封的價格排位指出，發現瑞銀（UBS）的利是封最受歡迎的，價格高達 10 元一個。排名第二的是瑞信（Credit Suisse），價格為每封 6.2 元；第三位是摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley），每封為 5.9 元。至於本地銀行龍頭的滙豐，每個利是封叫價 4 元，排名第六。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ubsred_packets_2022__1640866058_a634956f_progressive-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1083287" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ubsred_packets_2022__1640866058_a634956f_progressive-1-694x456.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ubsred_packets_2022__1640866058_a634956f_progressive-1-694x456.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ubsred_packets_2022__1640866058_a634956f_progressive-1-768x505.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ubsred_packets_2022__1640866058_a634956f_progressive-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1083265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-694x359.png" alt="" width="694" height="359" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-694x359.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-1280x662.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-768x397.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-1536x794.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58-2048x1059.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-12.52.58.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.53.48.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1083274" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.53.48-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.53.48-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.53.48-768x533.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.53.48.jpg 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.54.32.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1083275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.54.32-694x495.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.54.32-694x495.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.54.32-768x547.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-27-13.54.32.jpg 1118w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>雖然電子利是封因新冠疫情原因而被廣泛推廣，但設計精美的傳統紙製利是仍是主流。今年，瑞銀的利是封以老虎圖案作設計，材質採用特別的立體霧面，吸引喜歡收藏利是封的人士購買。</p><p>報導亦指，香港每年花費高達 3 億港元印刷利是封，而各投資銀行利是封設計亦越來越精緻。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-01-24/red-packets-from-global-banks-become-hong-kong-collectors-items">Bloomberg</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
